on","history":"/rest/api/content/3067052052/history","body":"","version":"","descendants":"/rest/api/content/3067052052/descendant","space":"/rest/api/space/BAN","childTypes":"","schedulePublishInfo":"","operations":"","schedulePublishDate":"","children":"/rest/api/content/3067052052/child","ancestors":"","draftVersion":""},"_links":{"self":"https://qubika.atlassian.net/wiki/rest/api/content/3067052052","tinyui":"/x/FIDPtg","editui":"/pages/resumedraft.action?draftId=3067052052","webui":"/spaces/BAN/pages/3067052052/Preautorizaciones+en+vpos","edituiv2":"/spaces/BAN/pages/edit-v2/3067052052"}}],"macroRenderedOutput":{},"body":{"storage":{"value":"<ac:structured-macro ac:name=\"info\" ac:schema-version=\"1\" ac:macro-id=\"e3f2be7e-c53d-4dbe-9703-bb0b91ddabab\"><ac:rich-text-body><p>Este documento contiene el tasking y la estimaci&oacute;n para la iniciativa <a href=\"https://bancard.atlassian.net/wiki/spaces/PV21/pages/470876200/Desarrollo+3ds+VPOS-PCI\">Desarrollo 3DS en VPos PCI</a></p></ac:rich-text-body></ac:structured-macro><table data-table-width=\"760\" data-layout=\"default\" ac:local-id=\"cf4223c2-6347-410f-a2bf-0412a5479a9b\"><colgroup><col style=\"width: 396.0px;\" /><col style=\"width: 110.0px;\" /><col style=\"width: 253.0px;\" /></colgroup><tbody><tr><th><p><strong>Tarea</strong></p></th><th><p><strong>Estimaci&oacute;n (hs)</strong></p></th><th><p><strong>Servicio / Portal</strong></p></th></tr><tr><td><p><span style=\"color: rgb(171,245,209);\">Agregar nuevos parametros opcionales a la operaci&oacute;n </span><code>pay_pci_encrypted_buy</code><span style=\"color: rgb(171,245,209);\"> (autorizacion y preautorizacion)</span></p></td><td><p><span style=\"color: rgb(171,245,209);\">4</span></p></td><td><p><span style=\"color: rgb(171,245,209);\">vpos-service</span></p></td></tr><tr><td><p><span style=\"color: rgb(171,245,209);\">Agregar nuevos parametros opcionales a la operaci&oacute;n </span><code>confirm_pci_preauthorization</code><span style=\"color: rgb(171,245,209);\"> (confirmar preautorizacion)</span></p></td><td><p><span style=\"color: rgb(171,245,209);\">4</span></p></td><td><p><span style=\"color: rgb(171,245,209);\">vpos-service</span></p></td></tr><tr><td><p><span style=\"color: rgb(171,245,209);\">Flujo de autoizacion: </span></p><ul><li><p><span style=\"color: rgb(171,245,209);\">Llamar a un nuevo endpoint jpos compras para buy encrypted (ser&aacute; igual al que ya se usa hoy pero con los par&aacute;metros nuevos) (operaci&oacute;n </span><code>pay_pci_encrypted_buy</code><span style=\"color: rgb(171,245,209);\">)</span></p></li></ul></td><td><p><span style=\"color: rgb(171,245,209);\">16</span></p></td><td><p><span style=\"color: rgb(171,245,209);\">vpos-service</span></p></td></tr><tr><td><p>Flujo de preautorizacion:</p><ul><li><p>Agregar nuevos par&aacute;metros para la llamada del rpg vprg005. (operaci&oacute;n<span style=\"color: rgb(171,245,209);\"> </span><code>pay_pci_encrypted_buy</code>)</p></li></ul></td><td><p>8</p></td><td><p>vpos-service</p></td></tr><tr><td><p>Flujo de confirmar preautorizacion:</p><ul><li><p>Agregar nuevos par&aacute;metros para la llamada del rpg vprg005 (operaci&oacute;n<span style=\"color: rgb(171,245,209);\"> </span><code>confirm_pci_preauthorization</code>)</p></li></ul></td><td><p>8</p></td><td><p>vpos-service</p></td></tr><tr><td><p><span style=\"color: rgb(171,245,209);\">Quitar operaci&oacute;n y todo lo relacionado a </span><code>pay_pci_buy</code><span style=\"color: rgb(171,245,209);\"> que no se utiliza mas. Representations, service, tests, etc.</span></p></td><td><p><span style=\"color: rgb(171,245,209);\">4</span></p></td><td><p><span style=\"color: rgb(171,245,209);\">vpos-service</span></p></td></tr></tbody></table><ac:adf-extension><ac:adf-node type=\"panel\"><ac:adf-attribute key=\"panel-type\">note</ac:adf-attribute><ac:adf-content><p>Preguntas</p></ac:adf-content></ac:adf-node><ac:adf-fallback><div class=\"panel conf-macro output-block\" style=\"background-color: rgb(234,230,255);border-color: rgb(153,141,217);border-width: 1.0px;\"><div class=\"panelContent\" style=\"background-color: rgb(234,230,255);\">\n<p>Preguntas</p>\n</div></div></ac:adf-fallback></ac:adf-extension><ol start=\"1\"><li><p>Nuevo endpoint de jpos. En qu&eacute; casos debe utilizarse el nuevo y en qu&eacute; casos se mantiene el actual?<br /><span style=\"color: rgb(0,102,68);\">El nuevo se utiliza para pci buy encrypted.</span><br /><span style=\"color: rgb(0,102,68);\">Ese mismo endpoint que se usa hoy en d&iacute;a en pci buy encrypted tambi&eacute;n se usa para el flujo de multibuy, esto se mantiene, solo se modifica el endpoint de pci buy encrypted por el nuevo que b&aacute;sicamente ser&aacute; el mismo pero la url diferente y tendr&aacute; los par&aacute;metros nuevos de 3ds.</span></p></li><li><p>Nuevo endpoint jpos y programa VPRG005: ante los nuevos par&aacute;metros que se le env&iacute;an. Hay nuevos c&oacute;digos de respuesta? Debe agregarse alguna l&oacute;gica nueva? Modificarse alg&uacute;n dato en la base de datos?<br /><span style=\"color: rgb(0,102,68);\">No hay l&oacute;gica nueva con respecto a la respuesta ni modificar alg&uacute;n dato de la base de datos</span></p></li><li><p>programa VPRG005: largo de los nuevos par&aacute;metros de entrada? Se modifican par&aacute;metros de salida?<br /><span style=\"color: rgb(0,102,68);\">Sobre los par&aacute;metros de entrada hoy les actualizamos los largos de los campos, y no se modifican los par&aacute;metros de salida, las respuestas seguir&aacute;n siendo iguales a las existentes hoy en d&iacute;a  </span></p></li></ol>","representation":"storage","embeddedContent":[],"_expandable":{"content":"/rest/api/content/3229319169"}},"_expandable":{"editor":"","atlas_doc_format":"","view":"","export_view":"","styled_view":"","dynamic":"","editor2":"","anonymous_export_view":""}},"extensions":{"position":1343},"_expandable":{"childTypes":"","container":"/rest/api/space/BAN","schedulePublishInfo":"","metadata":"","operations":"","schedulePublishDate":"","children":"/rest/api/content/3229319169/child","restrictions":"/rest/api/content/3229319169/restriction/byOperation","history":"/rest/api/content/3229319169/history","draftVersion":"","descendants":"/rest/api/content/3229319169/descendant","space":"/rest/api/space/BAN"},"_links":{"editui":"/pages/resumedraft.action?draftId=3229319169","webui":"/spaces/BAN/pages/3229319169/Desarrollo+3ds+VPOS-PCI+-+Tasking+y+Estimaci+n","edituiv2":"/spaces/BAN/pages/edit-v2/3229319169","context":"/wiki","self":"https://qubika.atlassian.net/wiki/rest/api/content/3229319169","tinyui":"/x/AYB7w","collection":"/rest/api/content","base":"https://qubika.atlassian.net/wiki"}}